Those of us in Europe, who continue to admire and look up at the achievements of entrepreneurship in the US, fully appreciate that what renders this video so emotionally powerful is that it in fact stands for all that is great about the USA. Free enterprise is the greatest driver of all human endeavor and, whatever views we may have on government politics, the US remains the shining beacon for the world. Neither the facts the video represents, nor the way it represents them could have been produced by any nation's state organization. The space race has been won, finally, and forever, by free individuals.
To the future of space and more!
